# Enforce LF line endings for all text files on every platform.
#
# The canonical registry index
# (crates/coven-runtime-registry/canonical/index.json) is byte-compared by the
# `committed_index_matches_sources` drift-guard test against the output of
# `conjure registry build`, which always writes LF. Without this, a Windows
# checkout (autocrlf) would rewrite the index to CRLF and fail the test
# spuriously. Pinning LF also keeps the embedded index bytes / SHA-256 identical
# across platforms.
* text=auto eol=lf
